they didn't know what to do.

00:17:26.733 --> 00:17:28.234
So they said, "All right, we'll raise your Kundalini."

00:17:29.109 --> 00:17:30.608
That's how they started doing it

00:17:30.817 --> 00:17:32.733
and it's helping now, [we were now,?]

00:17:33.025 --> 00:17:33.608
that you are doing it.

00:17:33.817 --> 00:17:35.150
Otherwise they would not touch it.

00:17:37.608 --> 00:17:39.525
So every disadvantage,

00:17:39.858 --> 00:17:43.150
every negativity is to be used for positivity.

00:17:43.441 --> 00:17:47.733
As I've told you before also an example of a little cell

00:17:48.025 --> 00:17:52.025
going inside the Mother Earth, sees a big boulder there,

00:17:52.275 --> 00:17:55.983
goes round it, [ties?] round it again and again and again

00:17:56.192 --> 00:18:00.691
and uses it for further holding of the tree,

00:18:00.983 --> 00:18:02.400
for the support of the tree.

00:18:04.234 --> 00:18:06.525
That is what is wisdom,

00:18:09.650 --> 00:18:11.650
that is what is wisdom

00:18:11.942 --> 00:18:18.025
and this wisdom comes through meditation,
meditative method.

00:18:18.359 --> 00:18:23.150
So you must everyday meditate and raise your Kundalini,

00:18:23.441 --> 00:18:25.566
otherwise you cannot grow by saying,

00:18:25.900 --> 00:18:26.817
"Mother, I love you,

00:18:27.109 --> 00:18:31.900
I love you," writing Me ten pages letters,

00:18:32.192 --> 00:18:33.900
which is impossible to read,

00:18:33.983 --> 00:18:37.359
doing all kinds of things like that

00:18:37.691 --> 00:18:40.400
and asking Me questions morning till evening.

00:18:41.150 --> 00:18:44.067
Nothing, nothing is going to help you

00:18:44.359 --> 00:18:46.983
to understand Me or to understand yourself

00:18:47.192 --> 00:18:48.483
or to understand Sahaja Yoga

00:18:48.775 --> 00:18:50.275
or to grow in Sahaja Yoga.

00:18:50.608 --> 00:18:53.483
You may talk, discuss, do what you like,

00:18:53.775 --> 00:18:57.192
to understand Sahaja Yoga best is to keep very happy.

00:18:57.483 --> 00:19:01.275
Happy faces, happiness within yourself,

00:19:01.566 --> 00:19:03.566
joy within yourself,

00:19:03.900 --> 00:19:06.900
try to see the essence of joy in everything,

00:19:07.192 --> 00:19:09.775
don't try to criticize, make yourself miserable.

00:19:10.983 --> 00:19:14.691
But to raise your Kundalini

00:19:14.983 --> 00:19:17.483
every morning religiously,

00:19:17.775 --> 00:19:20.983
every morning, every night raise your Kundalini.

00:19:21.317 --> 00:19:25.817
Kundalini is like the nourishment, the nourishment,

00:19:26.109 --> 00:19:32.483
the water of life for the growth of your inner being.

00:19:32.775 --> 00:19:34.608
If you do not meditate,

00:19:34.900 --> 00:19:36.900
if you do not know how to raise your Kundalini,

00:19:37.192 --> 00:19:38.691
you better try to learn it.

00:19:39.025 --> 00:19:41.608
Negative people always avoid that

00:19:41.900 --> 00:19:43.400
because then they feel burnings,

00:19:43.691 --> 00:19:46.067
they feel this. Face it up for a while,

00:19:46.067 --> 00:19:49.192
doesn't matter, face it up, clear out yourself

00:19:49.483 --> 00:19:52.109
and see that you raise your own Kundalini.

00:19:52.359 --> 00:19:55.109
Don't blame your husband, don't blame your wife,

00:19:55.359 --> 00:19:57.775
don't blame your children, don't blame your atmosphere,

00:19:58.067 --> 00:20:00.275
nothing of the kind. You can go in the jungles everyday,

00:20:00.566 --> 00:20:02.441
you can go anywhere you want to,

00:20:02.733 --> 00:20:04.150
if you want to do it, you can do it.

00:20:04.441 --> 00:20:07.817
But people must understand that now we are saints,

00:20:08.109 --> 00:20:10.192
and saints have to do that.

00:20:13.483 --> 00:20:15.566
You'll be surprised if you start meditating,

00:20:15.900 --> 00:20:18.275
most of your problems will disappear

00:20:18.566 --> 00:20:23.275
because all physical problems will be looked after by God.

00:20:23.566 --> 00:20:25.900
All material problems will be looked after.

00:20:26.192 --> 00:20:29.483
All other problems, family problems will be looked after.

00:20:29.775 --> 00:20:34.691
But the main problem is how to make you do it.

00:20:34.983 --> 00:20:41.067
It's like once you eat your food
your tongue can taste it,

00:20:41.317 --> 00:20:44.192
it gets the saliva, it goes down,

00:20:44.483 --> 00:20:45.483
it's all looked after,

00:20:45.691 --> 00:20:48.067
it goes down properly, down below it is all

00:20:48.359 --> 00:20:50.359
the juices are secreted,

00:20:50.483 --> 00:20:52.566
they know that the food is coming,

00:20:52.858 --> 00:20:57.067
it is digested in different parts, as it is, it is all built-in.

00:20:57.067 --> 00:20:59.150
But you must put it in the mouth,

00:21:03.359 --> 00:21:06.942
and this is what is the mechanism of Sahaja Yoga is

00:21:07.025 --> 00:21:11.650
that you must meditate and raise your Kundalini.

00:21:11.858 --> 00:21:15.441
In so many ways, in so many styles, in so many angles

00:21:15.775 --> 00:21:18.566
I have said this again and again and again and again.

00:21:20.775 --> 00:21:22.441
But that's what we do not do.

00:21:23.775 --> 00:21:26.942
And know your purpose, you must know your purpose.

00:21:27.275 --> 00:21:28.275
Like as I said

00:21:28.483 --> 00:21:31.483
that  the leaders do not know their importance at all.

00:21:32.775 --> 00:21:35.775
They behave sometimes in a manner which I can't understand.

00:21:37.067 --> 00:21:40.775
They become so silly about their wives, their husbands

00:21:41.109 --> 00:21:42.192
that I cannot understand.

00:21:42.483 --> 00:21:44.775
That's not important at all.

00:21:45.109 --> 00:21:47.691
If they're leaders, they have responsibility.

00:21:48.525 --> 00:21:51.525
Secondly, the leaders must tell off

00:21:51.733 --> 00:21:53.150
people who are to be told off,

00:21:53.441 --> 00:21:54.441
it's very important.

00:22:01.150 --> 00:22:03.775
If you cannot tell off people, it's no use.

00:22:05.858 --> 00:22:09.942
And that's how the leadership is not going to be respected,

00:22:10.275 --> 00:22:13.150
if you do not tell off people who are negative.

00:22:13.483 --> 00:22:16.983
One negative problem comes in, immediately they'll report it,

00:22:17.275 --> 00:22:18.608
I immediately know this is his wife

00:22:18.817 --> 00:22:20.400
or husband must be doing nonsense there.

00:22:20.691 --> 00:22:22.483
Immediately it is reported,

00:22:22.775 --> 00:22:24.275
"This is happening, that is happening,"

00:22:24.483 --> 00:22:26.275
is a sign of negativity.

00:22:27.983 --> 00:22:32.150
Immediately you can solve the problem, give bandhans.

00:22:35.525 --> 00:22:39.150
The simplest way is to sit before My photograph

00:22:39.359 --> 00:22:41.775
and just say, "Mother, please this is the problem," finished.

00:22:43.067 --> 00:22:45.025
There's no need to take a telephone and

00:22:45.317 --> 00:22:47.733
telephone to Me at about two o'clock in the night.

00:22:50.025 --> 00:22:53.441
Just do that, but the trouble is you cannot

00:22:53.733 --> 00:22:56.650
because your system is not yet reached that point.

00:22:57.983 --> 00:22:59.067
It's such a vicious circle.

00:22:59.359 --> 00:23:01.858
Your system must reach that point

00:23:02.150 --> 00:23:04.275
where the connection is absolutely there,

00:23:04.525 --> 00:23:06.566
you don't care for leadership, anything,

00:23:06.858 --> 00:23:09.109
but you care for your inner growth.

00:23:09.359 --> 00:23:12.691
If your inner growth is in that position

00:23:12.691 --> 00:23:15.275
it will happen automatically.

00:23:20.109 --> 00:23:22.359
This is what it is, very difficult

00:23:22.691 --> 00:23:26.983
for people to understand that we have to be

00:23:27.317 --> 00:23:30.067
sensibly placed towards ourselves.

00:23:32.067 --> 00:23:35.067
Now about the leaders I would say this about others also,

00:23:35.359 --> 00:23:40.275
that we have to be very, very sensibly

00:23:40.483 --> 00:23:42.192
placed about ourselves.

00:23:42.650 --> 00:23:45.150
Are we sensible towards ourselves?

00:23:45.441 --> 00:23:47.858
Some old people behave like children,

00:23:48.192 --> 00:23:50.525
some children behave like old people in the

00:23:50.733 --> 00:23:54.317
sense that start telling off, answering back, misbehaving.

00:23:54.650 --> 00:23:58.150
We must know our age, our group,

00:23:58.441 --> 00:24:02.817
everything and behave in a manner that is dignified.

00:24:03.109 --> 00:24:06.817
In a small age also if a child talks like a child,

00:24:07.359 --> 00:24:09.775
he can be very, very positive.

00:24:13.275 --> 00:24:16.566
I must tell you that I've had some very, very funny reports

00:24:16.858 --> 00:24:19.150
about some people which was so shocking

00:24:19.483 --> 00:24:22.275
that how did they arbitrarily behaved.

00:24:23.525 --> 00:24:27.858
And it's only thing that is behind is the sense of leadership.

00:24:28.441 --> 00:24:31.150
I wanted to be leaders, this wanted to be leaders,

00:24:31.441 --> 00:24:32.150
that wanted to be leaders.

00:24:32.525 --> 00:24:35.858
There's nothing like leadership in Sahaja Yoga,

00:24:36.067 --> 00:24:38.359
you don't know your Mother is too capable.

00:24:39.650 --> 00:24:43.359
She doesn't need any leaders, you don't know Her,

00:24:43.650 --> 00:24:46.775
better know Her. She's too capable,

00:24:46.817 --> 00:24:49.025
very clever and cunning woman.

00:24:58.317 --> 00:25:00.817
She's all-powerful

00:25:01.150 --> 00:25:03.234
and She knows everything about you,

00:25:03.566 --> 00:25:05.400
She knows how to handle situations.

00:25:05.691 --> 00:25:09.025
She's not going to allow Sahaja Yoga

00:25:09.317 --> 00:25:11.317
disappear because of somebody's stupidity.

00:25:11.525 --> 00:25:12.317
Know that!

00:25:14.900 --> 00:25:18.317
Sitting down here I know about everything about everyone.

00:25:18.900 --> 00:25:21.983
I may look very simple, it's not so.

00:25:27.983 --> 00:25:30.608
That's why I have to tell you

00:25:30.608 --> 00:25:33.775
that you don't consider yourself

00:25:34.109 --> 00:25:43.192
to be endowed with some sort of a special power as a leader.

00:25:43.483 --> 00:25:49.775
Only that you have the power through your Mother

00:25:50.067 --> 00:25:51.566
which you have to assert.

00:25:51.858 --> 00:25:54.359
So, "Whatever I'm doing is the Mother Who is doing it."

00:25:54.691 --> 00:25:56.566
And when you do that you'll be amazed

00:25:56.858 --> 00:25:59.942
that  whatever you want  will be sensible,

00:26:00.275 --> 00:26:02.942
whatever you'll ask for it will be sensible

00:26:03.275 --> 00:26:06.067
- sensible means which is related to Sahaja Yoga.

00:26:08.359 --> 00:26:10.359
And whatever you do will be sensible.

00:26:10.733 --> 00:26:14.317
All your dignity, everything will pile up together,

00:26:14.650 --> 00:26:18.441
but foremost thing and the most important at

00:26:18.691 --> 00:26:21.109
any cost you must meditate.

00:26:26.150 --> 00:26:30.067
This is what I have to now tell to our Indians also

00:26:30.359 --> 00:26:33.650
but for you it is very important

00:26:34.942 --> 00:26:37.775
because now you are returning back to

00:26:39.067 --> 00:26:40.441
"the real place."

00:26:44.775 --> 00:26:48.650
Like yesterday somebody said to Me,  some westerner said,

00:26:48.942 --> 00:26:51.566
"Mother they are talking about why you left Vaikuntha

00:26:51.858 --> 00:26:54.150
and came to this India,

00:26:54.483 --> 00:26:57.483
is all right, but we would say why did you leave this India

00:26:57.775 --> 00:26:58.775
and came to us."

00:27:01.650 --> 00:27:04.275
Then the answer was there that the God

00:27:04.775 --> 00:27:09.067
God has become mad about the saints

00:27:09.359 --> 00:27:10.525
because of the saints

00:27:10.817 --> 00:27:12.025
and their company.

00:27:12.317 --> 00:27:15.192
But the saints have to be saints

00:27:15.525 --> 00:27:17.192
otherwise they become troublesome to Me.

00:27:19.317 --> 00:27:22.691
If I go to lunatic asylum

00:27:23.025 --> 00:27:24.109
nothing will happen to Me.

00:27:25.691 --> 00:27:30.109
If I go to say, to a cemetery, nothing will happen to Me.

00:27:31.733 --> 00:27:35.359
But if a saint catches even a slightest thing,

00:27:35.691 --> 00:27:37.483
that troubles Me, tortures Me,

00:27:37.775 --> 00:27:39.691
not outwardly may be, but inside.

00:27:44.983 --> 00:27:47.983
Because I've given you place in My heart,

00:27:48.359 --> 00:27:51.067
in My being, you circulate in My being.

00:27:54.650 --> 00:27:56.483
That is how I know about you.

00:27:56.775 --> 00:27:59.275
So if you really grow better,

00:27:59.608 --> 00:28:01.983
if you improve better

00:28:02.275 --> 00:28:04.691
it will be a thing of joy for you

00:28:04.983 --> 00:28:06.942
and the greatest joy for Me as well,

00:28:07.234 --> 00:28:09.150
that's all I want that you should be,

00:28:09.441 --> 00:28:12.067
nothing else, nothing else.

00:28:13.900 --> 00:28:17.359
Now one more assurance I want to give you

00:28:17.691 --> 00:28:22.775
that we are going to start certain projects in India.

00:28:23.025 --> 00:28:24.900
Now the time has come,

00:28:25.192 --> 00:28:27.983
we have acquired some land definitely now

00:28:28.317 --> 00:28:30.317
and we are going to work out

00:28:30.608 --> 00:28:33.525
some projects as soon as I settle down in India,

00:28:33.817 --> 00:28:36.608
we will start showing the manifestation of that.

00:28:36.900 --> 00:28:39.608
And maybe this kind of tour

00:28:39.900 --> 00:28:44.400
I may not be able to do after a few years.

00:28:44.691 --> 00:28:48.317
But then you yourself will be able to conduct  these

00:28:48.650 --> 00:28:50.817
tours in your own country, go round

00:28:51.109 --> 00:28:53.983
because this is a training period where you will learn how

00:28:54.317 --> 00:28:55.691
to do this kind of thing.

00:28:56.025 --> 00:28:58.983
Of course in your country it's rather difficult to get such people

00:28:59.317 --> 00:29:02.608
but how to contact: I started with one person.

00:29:02.900 --> 00:29:06.691
So I'm just a lady, housewife

00:29:06.983 --> 00:29:09.317
and if I could do it, why not you?

00:29:21.025 --> 00:29:25.858
So now go with a pleasant mind, enjoy yourself.

00:29:27.858 --> 00:29:30.858
It's very difficult for a mother to bear all this because

00:29:31.150 --> 00:29:33.566
when I leave India I feel terrible about the Indians,

00:29:33.858 --> 00:29:35.608
when I leave youI feel terrible about you.

00:29:35.900 --> 00:29:36.817
It's something horrible

00:29:36.983 --> 00:29:39.691
that I want that somehow or other we all should have one

00:29:39.900 --> 00:29:44.900
huge country of our own where we all settle down happily together.

00:29:57.025 --> 00:30:01.192
So on behalf of you I would like to thank all the Indians

00:30:01.525 --> 00:30:04.025
who have done so much for us,

00:30:04.317 --> 00:30:07.359
given us all the comfort, according to them it was discomfort

00:30:07.691 --> 00:30:09.275
but according to you it was comfort.

00:30:29.359 --> 00:30:30.983
Now you are going on this tour,

00:30:31.275 --> 00:30:32.192
I would request you not to discuss

00:30:32.483 --> 00:30:37.192
other mundane nonsensical things on the way but

00:30:37.483 --> 00:30:39.441
discuss Sahaja Yoga. Understand,

00:30:39.733 --> 00:30:42.359
there are people who are just new, tell them  about Sahaj Yog,

00:30:42.650 --> 00:30:44.608
let them know what is Sahaja Yoga is,

00:30:44.900 --> 00:30:48.359
also explain to them what is Sahaja Yoga.

00:30:48.650 --> 00:30:51.192
You'll be travelling now quite a lot

00:30:51.483 --> 00:30:53.817
and also you'll be going to places where

00:30:53.983 --> 00:30:55.608
we are going to have our projects done.

00:30:55.900 --> 00:30:58.858
You can have a look at it, will be a good idea

00:30:59.150 --> 00:31:03.150
and also you think about what kind of projects

00:31:03.359 --> 00:31:05.359
we can have in this country

00:31:05.650 --> 00:31:11.234
which will help them to achieve better results in Sahaja Yoga.

00:31:12.109 --> 00:31:14.525
All these we have to discuss

00:31:14.817 --> 00:31:18.525
and this group is much more serious-type,

00:31:18.691 --> 00:31:21.608
I think, and it's going to work out something seriously.

00:31:22.441 --> 00:31:26.858
About the future plans that we would like to have

00:31:27.150 --> 00:31:31.067
here and abroad and whatever are the dates and

00:31:31.359 --> 00:31:34.608
things you would like to do. In the month of May, June, July

00:31:34.817 --> 00:31:37.317
I would be in the West and

00:31:37.608 --> 00:31:40.150
May  I would like to keep for America,

00:31:40.441 --> 00:31:43.150
if possible, at least the second half of May.

00:31:43.441 --> 00:31:46.109
The rest of it you can adjust it the way you want to have

00:31:46.441 --> 00:31:49.525
and also arrange your programs among yourselves

00:31:49.817 --> 00:31:51.733
whichever way you say is all right.

00:31:52.067 --> 00:31:55.067
This time it was desired that I should go to Greece,

00:31:55.359 --> 00:31:58.150
I don't mind, I would like to go there and do the needful.

00:32:09.733 --> 00:32:12.817
I hope all the leaders have got the [chains?]

00:32:13.109 --> 00:32:16.025
I have given to Warren.

00:32:18.317 --> 00:32:19.441
All right, it's done now.

00:32:21.150 --> 00:32:24.150
I worry about all little, little things like that.

